48ZUNmP0q23dkUUI6JXc3Mk_xUpUCwJVbD05O4=\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Evaluating metadata generation**\\n\\nI’m wondering if metadata is generated during dynamic reflection in the test code. It seems like there's an existing framework that combines the agent with tests, and I think we just need to add our test case. I’m considering if we require `@JsonCreator` in the org.codehaus.jackson.annotate package. Maybe I should also look at the build configurations, but I’m not sure if that’s necessary. Perhaps we can add a file if we have an unused placeholder.\"}]}"}, {"type": "toolCall", "id": "call_Gk4XLJuiMd25PqW75oaOhROn|fc_07249715962667740169f760da4c9c81a2848fd714be3a1f00", "name": "write", "arguments": {"path": "tests/src/org.codehaus.jackson/jackson-mapper-asl/1.8.3/src/test/java/org_codehaus_jackson/jackson_mapper_asl/CreatorInnerNumberBasedTest.java", "content": "/*\n * Copyright and related rights waived via CC0\n *\n * You should have received a copy of the CC0 legalcode along with this\n * work. If not, see <http://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/>.\n */\npackage org_codehaus_jackson.jackson_mapper_asl;\n\nimport org.codehaus.jackson.annotate.JsonCreator;\nimport org.codehaus.jackson.map.ObjectMapper;\nimport org.junit.jupiter.api.Test;\n\nimport static org.assertj.core.api.Assertions.assertThat;\n\npublic class CreatorInnerNumberBasedTest {\n    private final ObjectMapper objectMapper = new ObjectMapper();\n\n    @Test\n    void deserializesIntegerUsingSingleArgumentConstructor() throws Exception {\n        NumberFromIntConstructor value = objectMapper.readValue(\"37\", NumberFromIntConstructor.class);\n\n        assertThat(value.value).isEqualTo(37);\n    }\n\n    @Test\n    void deserializesIntegerUsingStaticFactoryMethod() throws Exception {\n        NumberFromIntFactory value = objectMapper.readValue(\"41\", NumberFromIntFactory.class);\n\n        assertThat(value.value).isEqualTo(41);\n    }\n\n    @Test\n    void deserializesLongUsingSingleArgumentConstructor() throws Exception {\n        NumberFromLongConstructor value = objectMapper.readValue(\"4294967296\", NumberFromLongConstructor.class);\n\n        assertThat(value.value).isEqualTo(4_294_967_296L);\n    }\n\n    @Test\n    void deserializesLongUsingStaticFactoryMethod() throws Exception {\n        NumberFromLongFactory value = objectMapper.readValue(\"4294967297\", NumberFromLongFactory.class);\n\n        assertThat(value.value).isEqualTo(4_294_967_297L);\n    }\n\n    public static final class NumberFromIntConstructor {\n        final int value;\n\n        @JsonCreator\n        public NumberFromIntConstructor(int value) {\n            this.value = value;\n        }\n    }\n\n    public static final class NumberFromIntFactory {\n        final int value;\n\n        private NumberFromIntFactory(int value) {\n            this.value = value;\n        }\n\n        @JsonCreator\n        public static NumberFromIntFactory fromJson(int value) {\n            return new NumberFromIntFactory(value);\n        }\n    }\n\n    public static final class NumberFromLongConstructor {\n        final long value;\n\n        @JsonCreator\n        public NumberFromLongConstructor(long value) {\n            this.value = value;\n        }\n    }\n\n    public static final class NumberFromLongFactory {\n        final long value;\n\n        private NumberFromLongFactory(long value) {\n            this.value = value;\n        }\n\n        @JsonCreator\n        public static NumberFromLongFactory fromJson(long value) {\n            return new NumberFromLongFactory(value);\n        }\n    }\n}\n"}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1373, "output": 1275, "cacheRead": 17408, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 20056, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1777819853318, "responseId": "resp_07249715962667740169f760cdae9c81a2b578